node.text:
🖤🖤 Wow!!! 🖤🖤⁠
⁠
🖤On this day 5 years ago, April 16th, 2016, we opened our doors and poured our first beer. We couldn’t have made it this far without you all, and we truly feel humbled by your faithfulness and support. This past year has been difficult for everyone and we’ve had to adapt constantly, but y’all have shown up for us over and over. 🖤 We have grown and learned so much in these last 5 years and will continue to push ourselves to try new things. Let’s do another 5 my babiez! 😝🖤⁠
⁠
🖤 All Anniversary beers are online now! Head on over to www.theveilbrewing.com/anniversary. We can’t wait to see you and celebrate this special milestone. Again, thank you from the bottom of our hearts. 🙏 🖤

⌛️☠️⚰️🐈 ACT I-III 🐈⚰️☠️⌛️⠀⠀
⠀⠀
⌛️☠️⚰️🐈 The pinnacle of our spirit barrel aged high gravity program is finally ready. 🖤 Sleeping Forever Grand Cru is a blend of 1, 2, and 3 year old Buffalo Trace bourbon barrel aged Sleeping Forever. It has an exceptionally refined depth of barrel character and flavor that only comes with time and careful blending of different vintages. Sleeping Forever Grand Cru will only be released every 5 years and is packaged in matte black bottles, waxed dipped, black velvet labels, wrapped in a custom handkerchief, and laid to rest in special individual boxes with a faux ostrich skin exterior and red velvet interior. 💀 New releases! 👻 ⁠
⁠⁠⁠
⚰️ RVA on Tuesday, 7/20 🐍 ⁠
🍑 NFK on Wednesday, 7/21🐅 ⁠
⁠
💀Tiger Skull🐅⁠
⁠
Tiger Skull is a brand new west coast inspired Red IPA brewed with Summit, Simcoe, and Chinook hops. Dank hoppiness with a sturdy malt backbone. 6.5% ABV. $14.50+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠⁠⁠
🦷 merciless merciless: enhanced 🐍 ⁠
⁠
merciless merciless: enhanced is the double dry-hopped rendition of merciless that gets the enhanced techniques to make it an even finer beer. Hopped in the whirlpool with Galaxy and Citra, then dry-hopped twice with the cool blend of Simcoe, Vic Secret, and Galaxy. We threw some Citra and Simcoe Cryo to bring it up a notch. Concentrated, extra soft impressions of gushers, grape flavored Big League Chew gum, and sweet tangerine slices. 8% ABV. $19.50+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
🥤The Plea 🍑 ⁠
⁠
The Plea is a brand new Sour Double IPA hopped with Galaxy then crushed with blackberry, apricot, peach, boysenberry, and milk sugar. Crushed with fruit, balanced by the Galaxy, and smoothed out perfectly by the milk sugar. 8% ABV. $22.00+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
🕷In Fear 👻 ⁠
⁠
⁠In Fear is a brand new IPA brewed with Strata, Nelson, Idaho 7, Citra, Motueka, and Citra Lupomax. Awesome complex hop profile displaying notes of gummy bears and fruit cocktails. 6% ABV. $14.50+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
⚰️ Buried Buried Alive Alive ⚰️ ⁠
⁠
Buried Buried Alive Alive is the double dry-hopped version of Buried Alive, the older sibling of Dirt Nap. The perfect combo of Galaxy, Citra, Nelson, and Mosaic hops. Creamy hoppy flavors of tropical tangerines and berries. 11% ABV. $20.00+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
📜Haunter🕯 ⁠
⁠
Haunter is a brand new American Stout. A great crusher pub-style Stout with way more drinkability than our Imperial Stout offerings. 5% ABV. $12.00+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
NO LIMITS. See y’all Tuesday for these 🔥
